item.title: CVE-2011-1070|2024-08-06T22:14:27.794Z -- v86d -- v86d
item.description: v86d before 0.1.10 do not verify if received netlink messages are sent by the kernel. This could allow unprivileged users to manipulate the video mode and potentially other consequences.
